<h4 id="goalkeeper-stats">Goalkeeper Stats</h4>
<blockquote>
  <p>Additionally, the goals against UCLA have to seep in somewhere, though redshirt senior goalie Garrett Danner is strong in nearly every zone. “Hot” zones where he and junior goalie Aleksandar Ruzic are blocking well are colored red, and “cold” zones where they aren’t are colored blue. For Danner’s save spread, the data is 83% accurate.</p>
</blockquote>
